2005-09-05  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	* example/core/script/webservice.js: SimpleSerializer now iterates over all element child nodes and 
	concats the node values to a single one (necessary cause Firefox splits strings > 4096 and inserts
	multiple DOM nodes).

2005-09-05  Michael Hartmeier  <mhm@schlund.de>

	* skel/build.xml: polish webapp target

2005-08-26  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/AbstractXMLServer.java (handleDocument): append timing info for getDom and handleDocument
	to the traillog.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ResultDocument.java (createIncludeFromStatusCode): no longer accept a "level" attribute.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java: put the "level" for errors and pagemessages into the 
	"error" or "message" tag, not to the pfx:include child.

