2005-01-28  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/generate/WebServiceTask.java: Improved modification
	checking. Now also changes in any class depending on the interface are detected and will
	cause a regeneration of the according descriptors and stubs.
	* skel/build.xml: The 'pfx-webservice' task has a new attribute 'builddir', which has to
	be set for dependency checking to work.

