2004-09-09  Martin Leidig <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added a new AppLoader feature, using the new AppLoader configuration property
	"apploader.package.exclude" you can specify certain packages which should not
	be loaded by the AppLoader even though their parent packages are.

	* example/common/conf/apploader.prop.in
	* skel/projects/common/conf/apploader.prop.in
        * src/de/schlund/pfixxml/loader/AppLoaderConfig.java

	Added new method isReloadableClass() to AppLoader class, which is responsible
	for the new extended class inclusion/exclusion mechanism, updated dependant
	classes.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/FactoryInitServlet.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/loader/AppClassLoader.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/loader/AppLoader.java

2004-09-01  Joerg Haecker <haecker@schlund.de>

	* fixes for rendering errors to screen

2004-08-25  Adam Habermann  <adam.habermann@schlund.de>

	"XML Schema validation"
	* example/core/schema/interfacewrapper200401.xsd
	Wrote an XML Schema for validating .iwrp files before transformation.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/*
	Included Validation in the ant tasks.
	* build.xml, skel/build.xml:
	Included Validation in ant build files. More specifically turned on validation
	for target "generate-src" (task pfx-iwrp). Validation is on by default, may be
	turned off via "-Dvalidation=false" (see ant -projecthelp).
	* src/**/*.iwrp
	Adapted existing .iwrp files to conform to the new schema validation. Changes:
	- The <interface> element must have a namespace declaration, must be tagged
	as an XML Schema instance and needs the xsi:schemaLocation attribute:
	<interface xmlns="http://pustefix.sourceforge.net/interfacewrapper200401"
	    xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
	    xsi:schemaLocation="http://pustefix.sourceforge.net/interfacewrapper200401
	    http://pustefix.sourceforge.net/interfacewrapper200401.xsd">
	- Only one <default> element is allowed to appear within a <param> element.
	The <default> element accepts one or more <value> elements. For Example:
	old: <default value="foo"/><default value="bar"/>
	new: <default><value>foo</value><value>bar</value></default>

2004-08-18 Joerg Haecker <haecker@schlund.de>

        * src/de/schlund/pfixxml/exceptionprocessor:
        -UniversalExceptionProcessor.java, util/ExceptionDataValue.java,
        util/XMLCreatorVisitor.java: cosmetics
        * src/de/schlund/pfixxml/exceptionprocessor/util/TextCreatorVisitor.java:
        Bugfix: fixed IndexOutOfBoundsException when handling java.lang.Error

