	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XSLVirtualTarget.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testenv/RecordManager.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testenv/RecordManagerFactory.java
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor/EditorProductFactoryTest.java
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGeneratorTest.java
	The big docroot cleanup. Not completely done, need to rethink what to do with config files
	for apache that really needs absolute file names.  Other than that, the editor seems to work,
	but the editor APPLET is broked. Which is no big problem, as we want to kill it anyway soon.

