2002-11-22  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* released 0.1.18

	* example/core/xsl/navigation.xsl.in: Massive Speed-Ups ~10x ....

2002-11-22  Volker Zaich <zaich@schlund.de>

	* example/core/xsl/include.xsl.in
